    "detailHtml": "<h2><strong>Precision in compact form</strong></h2>\n<p>The HGT Mini Alloy GTR (1:43) is a fully proportional 4WD drift car built with a full alloy body shell for a premium feel and realistic scale detailing. Designed for indoor drifting and tight spaces, this compact machine delivers controlled slides and smooth handling without needing a large track.</p>\n<p>Small in size. Serious in build quality.</p>\n<h2>What Makes The 1:43 Alloy Edition Different?</h2>\n<p>Unlike larger models that focus on size, the 1:43 Alloy Edition focuses on compact precision and premium detailing.</p>\n<p>• Full metal body construction<br>• Designed for indoor drifting<br>• Easier to control in tight spaces<br>• Realistic GTR styling in display-friendly scale</p>\n<p>This model is built for controlled, close-range drifting — not open ground racing.</p>\n<h3>Full Alloy Body Shell</h3>\n<p>Metal construction gives this model a heavier, more premium feel compared to standard plastic or fiber models.</p>\n<h3>Compact 1:43 Scale</h3>\n<p>Fits in your palm — perfect for desk setups, bedrooms, and indoor drifting.</p>\n<h3>4WD Drift System</h3>\n<p>Balanced traction allows smooth slides on tiles, marble, and smooth floors.</p>\n<h3>Full Proportional Control (2.4GHz)</h3>\n<p>Throttle and steering respond smoothly — not just basic left/right movement.</p>\n<h3>High-Speed 3.7V System</h3>\n<p>Powered by a 3.7V 180mAh rechargeable battery with strong acceleration for its size.</p>\n<h3>LED Headlights</h3>\n<p>Adds realism and a clean night-drift look.</p>\n<h3>Ready-To-Run (RTR)</h3>\n<p>Charge it, insert batteries in the remote, and start drifting.</p>\n<h2>WHO IS THIS FOR?</h2>\n<p>• First-time RC drift buyers<br>• Collectors who prefer detailed alloy models<br>• Indoor drift setups<br>• Gifting option with premium finish<br>• Apartment-friendly use</p>\n<h3><strong>Specifications</strong></h3>\n<p>Scale: 1:43<br>Drive Type: 4WD<br>Control System: 2.4GHz proportional<br>Motor: 615 high-speed motor<br>Battery: 3.7V 180mAh rechargeable<br>Charging: USB cable included<br>Control Range: Approx. 30–40 meters<br>Lighting: LED headlights<br>Recommended Surface: Smooth indoor floors</p>\n<h1>WHAT’S IN THE BOX</h1>\n<p>• 1 × 1:43 Alloy RC Drift Car<br>• 1 × 2.4GHz Remote Controller<br>• 1 × USB Charging Cable<br>• 1 × Rechargeable Battery (installed)<br>• Extra Drift Tires<br>• Mini Cones / Accessories (as shown)<br>• User Manual</p>",
