    "detailHtml": "<ul>\n<li>\n<h2>Stunts, Smoke &amp; Total Control</h2>\n<p>The <strong>4WD RC Drift Stunt Car with Smoke Spray</strong> is built for action-packed fun, combining drifting, spinning, and stunt driving with exciting visual effects. Designed for kids and young RC enthusiasts, this car delivers <strong>easy controls, wild stunts, and interactive play</strong> using both a standard remote and a <strong>gesture sensor watch</strong>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Key Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>4WD All-Direction Drive</strong> – Move forward, backward, sideways, rotate 360°, and perform drift stunts with ease</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Gesture Sensor Watch Control</strong> – Control the car using hand movements for a futuristic driving experience</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Smoke Spray Effect</strong> – Built-in spray function adds realistic smoke visuals during play</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>LED Headlights &amp; Light Wheels</strong> – Bright LED lighting enhances night-time play and visual excitement</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Dual Speed &amp; Stunt Modes</strong> – Switch between normal driving and stunt action at the press of a button</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Unique Drift Wheels</strong> – Special non-slip wheels with small pulleys allow smooth drifting and lateral movement on multiple surfaces</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Designed for Easy Play</h2>\n<p>Simple controls make this RC car <strong>easy to operate</strong>, even for first-time users. Kids can quickly learn how to perform spins, drifts, and stunt maneuvers without complex setup.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Where You Can Use It</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Indoor floors</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Outdoor concrete &amp; tiles</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Smooth roads and play areas</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>(Not recommended for water or rough off-road terrain.)</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Specifications</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Drive System:</strong> 4WD</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Control Modes:</strong> Remote Control + Gesture Sensor Watch</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Battery (Car):</strong> 3.7V 500mAh Li-Po (Rechargeable, Included)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Battery (Remote):</strong> 1× 1.5V AA Battery (Not Included)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Charging Time:</strong> ~45 minutes before first use</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Recommended Age:</strong> 5–12 years</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>What’s in the Box</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>1 × RC Drift Stunt Car</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>1 × Remote Controller</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>1 × Gesture Sensor Watch</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>1 × Rechargeable Battery</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>1 × USB Charging Cable</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Perfect Gift Choice</h2>\n<p>An exciting gift option for birthdays, festivals, or everyday fun—designed to keep kids <strong>active, engaged, and away from screens</strong>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Support &amp; Assurance</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Cash on Delivery available</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p> </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>",
